Skills.Name: Eternal Plum Blossom
Skills.Description: Recovers HP of all allies within 150 cm of ally with lowest HP by <color=red>{0}%</color> of ATK. Raises CRIT Rate of all Shadow Garden allies by <color=red>{2}%</color> for 30s. Recovers own SP by 200.00.
Skills.ShortDescription: Recovers HP of all allies within range. Raises CRIT Rate of all Shadow Garden allies. Recovers own SP

Skills.Name: Let Me Bless You
Skills.Description: Raises DMG Received for all enemies by <color=red>{0}%</color> for 15s. Also inflicts <code=400,param=256><color=#3398f1>Weakness</color> (150.00% of skill user's ATK) for 8s. Further cancels 2x Buff effects if Yellow Elemental.
Skills.ShortDescription: Raises DMG Received, inflicts Weakness on all enemies, cancels Buff effect(s) if Yellow Elemental
